content:
# FUNCTIONS ------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
amort_form <- function(pbal_tz_zz, pbal_zz, ann_r_zz, term_zz, in_grace_per_zz = 0) {
  mon_r <- ann_r_zz/12
  mon_n <- term_zz
  num <- mon_r * (1+mon_r)^mon_n
  den <- (1+mon_r)^mon_n -1 
  payment <- pbal_tz_zz * num / den # payment is determined only at the starting balance? 
  r_accr <- pbal_zz * mon_r
  bal_pmt <- payment - r_accr
  
  int_pmt <- r_accr
  
  if(in_grace_per_zz == 1){
    payment <- 0 
    bal_pmt <- 0 
    int_pmt <- 0 
  }
  new_pbal <- pbal_zz + r_accr - payment
  
  return(c(round(payment,2),round(bal_pmt,2) , round(int_pmt,2), round(r_accr,2), round(new_pbal,2)))
}

#amort_form(102240.11,102240.11,.15,48-3)

# How to find the rate givent he monthly payment and duration
find_rate <- function(principal_zz, payment_zz, term_zz){
  f <- function(r) (principal_zz *r / (1-(1+r)^term_zz) ) - payment_zz 
  sol <- uniroot(f, interval = c(1e-6,1))
  return(annual_rate = sol$root*100*12)
}

# mortgage   <- 300000
# duration   <- 360
# ann <- 1108.86
# uniroot(function(x) mortgage * x/12 / (1 - (1+x/12)^(-duration)) - ann,
#         c(1e-6,1))$root * 100
# 
# find_rate(principal_zz = mortgage,payment_zz = ann, term_zz= -1*duration )

amort_time_form <- function(start_date_zz,  pbal_zz, ann_r_zz, term_zz, grace_period_zz = 3) {
  pbal_tz_zz <-   pbal_zz
  mon_r <- ann_r_zz/12
  mon_n <- term_zz
  num <- mon_r * (1+mon_r)^mon_n
  den <- (1+mon_r)^mon_n -1 
  payment <- pbal_tz_zz * num / den
  r_accr <- pbal_zz * mon_r
  bal_pmt <- payment - r_accr
  
  new_pbal <- pbal_zz + r_accr - payment
  #return(new_pbal)
  new_pbal <- pbal_tz_zz
  
  amort_df <- data.frame(
    month = 0
    #, date = as.Date(start_date_zz)
    , payment = 0
    , principal = 0
    , interest = 0
    , interest_accrued = 0 
    , balance = pbal_tz_zz
  )
  
  i <- 1
  #d <- 
  
  while ( i <= term_zz) {
    
    
    if(i <=grace_period_zz) {
      in_grace <- 1
      term <- term_zz
    } else if (i == grace_period_zz +1) {
      # In this period we recalculate monthly payment
      pbal_tz_zz <- as.numeric(amort_df$balance[nrow(amort_df)])
      term <- term_zz - grace_period_zz 
      in_grace <-0
    } else {
      in_grace <-0
    }
    
    
    
    # Create the next line and add it on to existing data
    newrow <- amort_form(pbal_tz_zz, new_pbal,ann_r_zz,term, in_grace_per_zz =in_grace)
    newrow <- c(i,newrow)
    #, '2000-01-01' 
    amort_df <- rbind(amort_df,newrow)
    
    # can't get the dates to work right
    #amort_df$date[i] <- as.Date(ymd(as.Date(start_date_zz))) %m+% months(i-1)
    
    # Reset the starting balance
    new_pbal <- as.numeric(amort_df$balance[nrow(amort_df)])
    i <- i + 1
  }
  
  # Dates are still wonky
  #amort_df$date[term_zz] <- as.Date(ymd(as.Date(start_date_zz))) %m+% months(term_zz-1)
  
  # formats are also wonky
  amort_df <- amort_df %>%
    mutate(payment = as.numeric(payment)
           , principal = as.numeric(principal)
           , interest = as.numeric(interest)
           , balance = as.numeric(balance) 
    )
  return(amort_df)
}

name: R/calculate_cashflows.R
content:
nii_table_fun <- function( legal_fees_zz, op_de_comp_est_pct_zz
                           , ann_rate_zz = NA, loan_term_zz, grace_period_zz, markup_zz, down_payment_pct_zz
                           , seguro_est_pct_zz = NA , seguro_defl_rate_zz
                           , maint_premium_zz, maint_cost_per_visit_pct_zz = NA, maint_infl_zz
                           , costo_activo_zz,  costs_zz , albedo_wacc_zz, risk_free_rate_zz
                           , area_zz = 'Guatemala', risk_level_zz = 'Low', target_margin_zz = 0 
){
  
  
  # Lookup Fields 
  iva_rate <-pricing_info_table$GeographyTable$`TaxRate`[which(pricing_info_table$GeographyTable == area_zz)] 
  
  if (is.na(seguro_est_pct_zz )){
    seguro_pct <- pricing_info_table$GeographyTable$`Insurance`[which(pricing_info_table$GeographyTable$Area == area_zz)]   
  } else {
    seguro_pct <- seguro_est_pct_zz
  }
  
  if (is.na(maint_cost_per_visit_pct_zz )){
    maint_cost_per_visit_pct <- pricing_info_table$GeographyTable$`Maintenance`[which(pricing_info_table$GeographyTable$Area == area_zz)]   
  } else {
    maint_cost_per_visit_pct <- maint_cost_per_visit_pct_zz
  }
  
  ## recommended APR 
  rec_apr <-  calc_rec_apr(risk_level_zz, target_margin_zz,down_payment_pct_zz , loan_term_zz, albedo_wacc_zz) 
  
  if(is.na(ann_rate_zz)) {
    annual_APR <- rec_apr
  } else {
    annual_APR <- ann_rate_zz
  }
  
  
  
  # Calculated Fields  
  maint_cost_per_visit <- maint_cost_per_visit_pct*costo_activo_zz
  seguro_start <- grace_period + 1
  
  retail_price <- costo_activo_zz*(1+markup_zz)
  down_payment_amt <-  retail_price*down_payment_pct_zz
  principal <- retail_price*(1-down_payment_amt)
  monthly_rate <- annual_APR/12
  
  seguro_cost_est <- costo_activo_zz*seguro_pct ## Seguro 
  op_de_comp <- retail_price*op_de_comp_est_pct_zz
  
  
  
  finance_table <- amort_time_form('2000-01-01',principal,annual_APR,loan_term_zz,grace_period_zz)  
  
  df <- finance_table %>%
    mutate(
      enganche = ifelse(month == 0, down_payment_amt, 0)
      , legal_fees = ifelse(month == 0, legal_fees_zz, 0)
      , op_de_comp = ifelse(month== loan_term_zz, op_de_comp,0)
      
      , cost_seguro = ifelse((12-seguro_start+month) %% 12 != 0,0 
                             , ifelse(month>loan_term_zz,0
                                      , seguro_cost_est*seguro_defl_rate_zz^(floor(month/12))
                             ))
      
      , cost_maint = ifelse(month <= 24,0  ## Doesn't cost anything for first 2 years
                            ,ifelse(month> loan_term_zz, 0
                                    ,ifelse(month %% 12 != 0, 0
                                            ,maint_cost_per_visit*(1+maint_infl_zz)^(pmax(floor(month / 12 - 3), 0))
                                    )))
      , other_costs =
        ifelse(month==0,costs_zz*commission_expense_m1,
               ifelse(month==1,costs_zz*commission_expense_m2,
                      ifelse(month==2,costs_zz*commission_expense_m3
                             ,0)))
    )
  
  # Calculate the maintenence and insurance payments
  total_main_cost <- sum(df$cost_maint)*(1+maint_premium_zz)
  maint_pymnt <-  total_main_cost/(loan_term_zz-seguro_start+1)
  total_seguro_cost <- sum(df$cost_seguro)
  seguro_pymnt <-  total_seguro_cost/(loan_term_zz-seguro_start+1)
  
  df <- df |> 
    mutate(
      , seguro_pymnt = ifelse(month >= seguro_start & month <= loan_term_zz, seguro_pymnt,0)
      , maint_pymnt = ifelse(month >= seguro_start & month <= loan_term_zz, maint_pymnt,0)
      , income_lease = payment + enganche + op_de_comp
      , income_wservicios = income_lease + seguro_pymnt + legal_fees + maint_pymnt
      
      #, total_monthly_payment = payment + seguro + legal_fees + enganche + op_de_comp
      , iva = income_wservicios*iva_rate
      , income_total = income_wservicios + iva
      , capital_costs =
        ifelse(month==0,costo_activo_zz*activo_expense_m1,
               ifelse(month==1,costo_activo_zz*activo_expense_m2,
                      ifelse(month==2,costo_activo_zz*activo_expense_m3
                             ,0)))
      , debt_balance = ifelse(month==0, costo_activo_zz*activo_expense_m1 + other_costs -( payment + enganche + op_de_comp),NA)
      
      , income_qb = income_lease + seguro_pymnt + legal_fees  ## QB doessn't count maint income for some reason
      , iva_payment_qb = income_qb*iva_rate
    ) 
  
  for_iva <- (sum(df$income_wservicios) - (sum(df$capital_costs) - sum(df$other_costs) ))*iva_rate/(1+iva_rate)/(loan_term_zz-seguro_start)
  for_iva_qb <- (sum(df$income_qb) - (sum(df$capital_costs) - sum(df$other_costs) ))*iva_rate/(1+iva_rate)/(loan_term_zz-seguro_start)
  ## wtf is this tax calculation
  
  df <- df |>
    mutate(
      cost_iva = ifelse(month >= seguro_start & month <= loan_term_zz, for_iva,0)
      , cost_iva_qb = ifelse(month >= seguro_start & month <= loan_term_zz, for_iva_qb,0)
      , expense_qb = capital_costs + other_costs + cost_iva_qb + cost_maint + cost_seguro
      , debt_balance_qb = ifelse(month==0,expense_qb - income_qb,NA)
    )
  
  # calculate debt cost
  for(i in 2:loan_term_zz){
    df$debt_balance[i] = (df$debt_balance[i-1] + df$capital_costs[i]  - df$income_lease[i])*(1+albedo_wacc_zz/12) # Taking lease income rather than income_wservicios
    df$debt_balance_qb[i] = (df$debt_balance_qb[i-1] + df$expense_qb[i]  - df$income_qb[i])*(1+albedo_wacc_zz/12) # Taking lease income
  }
  
  df <- df |>
    mutate(
      lag_db = lag(debt_balance,1),
      , debt_cost = pmax(lag_db*(albedo_wacc_zz/12),0)
      , debt_cost = ifelse(month==0,0,debt_cost)
      , debt_cost_qb = pmax(debt_balance_qb*(albedo_wacc_zz/12),0)
    ) |>
    select(-c(lag_db))
  
  # calculate inflows and out-flows
  df <- df |>
    mutate(
      , expense_lease = capital_costs + other_costs
      , expense_lease_wdebt = expense_lease  +  debt_cost
      , expense_wservicios = expense_lease_wdebt + cost_maint + cost_seguro
      , expense_total = expense_wservicios + cost_iva  # currently IVA is in and out 
      
      , nii_lease = income_lease - expense_lease
      , nii_lease_wdebt = income_lease - expense_lease_wdebt
      , nii_wservicios = income_wservicios - expense_wservicios
      , nii_total = income_total - expense_total
      
      , cum_nii_lease = cumsum(nii_lease)
      , cum_nii_lease_wdebt = cumsum(nii_lease_wdebt)
      , cum_nii_wservicios = cumsum(nii_wservicios)
      , cum_nii_total = cumsum(nii_total)
      
      # this makes things easier for duration calc
      , pos_nii_lease_mon = ifelse(cum_nii_lease<0,9999,month)
      , pos_nii_lease_wdebt_mon = ifelse(cum_nii_lease_wdebt<0,9999,month)
      , pos_nii_wservicios_mon = ifelse(cum_nii_wservicios<0,9999,month)
      , pos_nii_total_mon = ifelse(cum_nii_total<0,9999,month)
    )
  
  # NPV
  df <- df |>
    mutate(
      discount_fact = 1/(1+ (risk_free_rate_zz/12))^month
      , npv_nii_lease = discount_fact*nii_lease
      , npv_nii_lease_wdebt = discount_fact*nii_lease_wdebt
      , npv_nii_wservicios = discount_fact*nii_wservicios
      , npv_nii_total = discount_fact*nii_total
    )
  
  
  return(df)
}

## Example
# 
# # Global Options 
# iva_rate <- 0.12
# albedo_wacc <- 0.10
# risk_free_rate <- 0.04
# seguro_defl_rate <- 0.96
# seguro_est_pct <- 0.017
# op_de_comp_est_pct <- 0.01
# commission_cost_est <- 0.023
# 
# maint_cost_per_visit_est_pct <- 0.028
# maint_inflation_rate_pct <- 0.05
# 
# # Timing for cost de activo --- not sure if this is constant across all loans?
# activo_expense_m1 <- 0.5
# activo_expense_m2 <- 0.4
# activo_expense_m3 <- 0.1
# 
# commission_expense_m1 <- 0.8
# commission_expense_m2 <- 0
# commission_expense_m3 <- 0.2
# 
# 
# # Loan Info  / Client Options
# costo_activo <- 398931
# down_payment_pct <- 0.00
# term_months <- 74
# grace_period <- 2 
# legal_fees <- 2350
# 
# 
# # Pricing Strat 
# markup <- 0.0124
# ann_rate <- 0.1842
# maint_premium <- 0.1
# target_margin <- 0.05

# nii_tab <- nii_table_fun(
#   ann_rate_zz = ann_rate
#   , grace_period_zz = grace_period
#   , markup_zz = markup
#   , down_payment_pct_zz = down_payment_pct
#   , legal_fees_zz = legal_fees
#   , op_de_comp_est_pct_zz = op_de_comp_est_pct
#   #, seguro_est_pct_zz = seguro_est_pct
#   , loan_term_zz = term_months
#   , area_zz = 'GT'
#   , costo_activo_zz = costo_activo
#   , costs_zz = other_costs
#   , albedo_wacc_zz = albedo_wacc
#   , risk_free_rate_zz = risk_free_rate

#   , maint_infl_zz = maint_inflation_rate_pct

name: R/calculate_kpis.R
content:
get_kpis <- function(nii_tab) {
  
  names <- c("Leasing", "Leasing w Debt", "w Servicios", "Total w IVA", "Total QB")
  income <- c(sum(nii_tab$income_lease), sum(nii_tab$income_lease), sum(nii_tab$income_wservicios), sum(nii_tab$income_total),sum(nii_tab$total_received_qb) )
  expense <- c(sum(nii_tab$expense_lease), sum(nii_tab$expense_lease_wdebt), sum(nii_tab$expense_wservicios), sum(nii_tab$expense_total) , sum(nii_tab$expense_total_qb))
  profit <- income-expense
  npv <- c(sum(nii_tab$npv_nii_lease), sum(nii_tab$npv_nii_lease_wdebt), sum(nii_tab$npv_nii_wservicios), sum(nii_tab$npv_nii_total), sum(nii_tab$npv_nii_total_qb) )
  irr <- c(round(jrvFinance::irr(nii_tab$nii_lease)*12*100,1), round(jrvFinance::irr(nii_tab$nii_lease_wdebt)*12*100,1), round(jrvFinance::irr(nii_tab$nii_wservicios)*12*100,1), round(jrvFinance::irr(nii_tab$nii_total)*12*100,1), round(jrvFinance::irr(nii_tab$nii_total_qb)*12*100,1))
  gross_margin <- (profit/expense)*100
  payback_period <- c(min(nii_tab$pos_nii_lease_mon), min(nii_tab$pos_nii_lease_wdebt_mon), min(nii_tab$pos_nii_wservicios_mon), min(nii_tab$pos_nii_total_mon), min(nii_tab$pos_nii_total_mon_qb))
  
  monthly_payment <- rep(nii_tab |> filter(month == 5) |> pull(payment), length(names))
  
  KPI_table <- rbind(
    income <- income
    , expense <- expense
    , profit <- income-expense
    , npv <- npv
    , irr <- irr
    , gross_margin <- gross_margin
    , payback_period <- payback_period
    , monthly_payment <-monthly_payment 
  )
  
  kpis <- c("Income", "Expense", "Profit", "NetPresentValue", "IRR", "Gross.Margin", "Payback.Period", "Monthly.Payment")
  KPI_table <- as.data.frame(KPI_table) |> mutate_if(is.numeric,round, 1)
  KPI_table <- cbind(kpis, KPI_table)
  
  
  names(KPI_table) <-  c("KPI", "Leasing", "Leasing w Debt", "w Servicios", "Total w IVA", "Total QB")
  return(KPI_table)
  
}

#' Calculate the cashflows for any project given minimal inputs


calculate_cashflows_fun <- function( legal_fees_zz, op_de_comp_est_pct_zz
                               , ann_rate_zz = NA, loan_term_zz, grace_period_zz, markup_zz, down_payment_pct_zz
                               , seguro_est_pct_zz = NA , seguro_defl_rate_zz
                               , maint_premium_zz, maint_cost_per_visit_pct_zz = NA, maint_infl_zz
                               , costo_activo_zz,  costs_zz , albedo_wacc_zz, risk_free_rate_zz
                               , area_zz = 'Guatemala', risk_level_zz = 'Low', target_margin_zz = 0 
){
  
  
  # Lookup Fields 
  iva_rate <-pricing_info_table$GeographyTable$`TaxRate`[which(pricing_info_table$GeographyTable == area_zz)] 
  
  if (is.na(seguro_est_pct_zz )){
    seguro_pct <- pricing_info_table$GeographyTable$`Insurance`[which(pricing_info_table$GeographyTable$Area == area_zz)]   
  } else {
    seguro_pct <- seguro_est_pct_zz
  }
  
  if (is.na(maint_cost_per_visit_pct_zz )){
    maint_cost_per_visit_pct <- pricing_info_table$GeographyTable$`Maintenance`[which(pricing_info_table$GeographyTable$Area == area_zz)]   
  } else {
    maint_cost_per_visit_pct <- maint_cost_per_visit_pct_zz
  }
  
  
  
  # Calculated Fields  
  maint_cost_per_visit <- maint_cost_per_visit_pct*costo_activo_zz
  seguro_start <- grace_period_zz + 1
  
  retail_price <- costo_activo_zz*(1+markup_zz)
  down_payment_amt <-  retail_price*down_payment_pct_zz
  principal <- retail_price- down_payment_amt
  monthly_rate <- ann_rate_zz/12
  
  seguro_cost_est <- costo_activo_zz*seguro_pct ## Seguro 
  op_de_comp <- retail_price*op_de_comp_est_pct_zz
  
  
  ## recommended APR 
  rec_apr <-  calc_rec_apr(risk_level_zz, target_margin_zz,down_payment_amt , loan_term_zz, albedo_wacc_zz) 
  
  if(is.na(ann_rate_zz)) {
    annual_APR <- rec_apr
  } else {
    annual_APR <- ann_rate_zz
  }
  
  # Ian's version currently doesn't include commission costs into the balance (i.e. no interest is charged for commission cost)
  finance_table <- amort_time_form('2000-01-01',principal,annual_APR,loan_term_zz,grace_period_zz)  
  
  df <- finance_table %>%
    mutate(
      enganche = ifelse(month == 0, down_payment_amt, 0)
      , legal_fees = ifelse(month == 0, legal_fees_zz, 0)
      , op_de_comp = ifelse(month== loan_term_zz, op_de_comp,0)
      
      , cost_seguro = ifelse((12-seguro_start+month) %% 12 != 0,0 
                             , ifelse(month>loan_term_zz,0
                                      , seguro_cost_est*seguro_defl_rate_zz^(floor(month/12))
                             ))
      
      , cost_maint = ifelse(month <= 24,0  ## Doesn't cost anything for first 2 years
                            ,ifelse(month> loan_term_zz, 0
                                    ,ifelse(month %% 12 != 0, 0
                                            ,maint_cost_per_visit*(1+maint_infl_zz)^(pmax(floor(month / 12 - 3), 0))
                                    )))
      , other_costs =
        ifelse(month==0,costs_zz*commission_expense_m1,
               ifelse(month==1,costs_zz*commission_expense_m2,
                      ifelse(month==2,costs_zz*commission_expense_m3
                             ,0)))
    )
  
  # Calculate the maintenence and insurance payments
  total_main_cost <- sum(df$cost_maint)*(1+maint_premium_zz)
  maint_pymnt <-  total_main_cost/(loan_term_zz-seguro_start+1)
  total_seguro_cost <- sum(df$cost_seguro)
  seguro_pymnt <-  total_seguro_cost/(loan_term_zz-seguro_start+1)
  
  df <- df |> 
    mutate(
      , seguro_pymnt = ifelse(month >= seguro_start & month <= loan_term_zz, seguro_pymnt,0)
      , maint_pymnt = ifelse(month >= seguro_start & month <= loan_term_zz, maint_pymnt,0)
      , costo_activo = costo_activo_zz
      , loan_term = loan_term_zz,
      , country_name = area_zz
    )
  return(df)
}

#' Example
# partial_table <- calculate_cashflows_fun(
#   ann_rate_zz = ann_rate
#   , grace_period_zz = grace_period
#   , markup_zz = markup
#   , down_payment_pct_zz = down_payment_pct
#   , legal_fees_zz = legal_fees
#   , op_de_comp_est_pct_zz = op_de_comp_est_pct
#   , seguro_est_pct_zz = seguro_est_pct
#   , loan_term_zz = term_months
#   , area_zz = 'GT'
#   , costo_activo_zz = costo_activo
#   , costs_zz = other_costs
#   , albedo_wacc_zz = albedo_wacc
#   , risk_free_rate_zz = risk_free_rate
#   , maint_cost_per_visit_pct_zz = maint_cost_per_visit_est_pct
#   , maint_infl_zz = maint_inflation_rate_pct
#   , maint_premium_zz = maint_premium
#   , seguro_defl_rate_zz = seguro_defl_rate
#   
# ) |>

#' Calculate income and expense from cashflow table

calculate_inc_exp_fun <- function(df_zz, loan_term_zz, grace_period_zz, risk_free_rate_zz, albedo_wacc_zz
                                  ,activo_expense_m1_zz = 0.6, activo_expense_m2_zz=0.3, activo_expense_m3_zz=0.1){
  seguro_start <- grace_period_zz + 1
  iva_rate <- pricing_info_table$GeographyTable$`TaxRate`[which(pricing_info_table$GeographyTable == df_zz$country_name)] 
  
  
  df <- df_zz |> 
    mutate(
      income_lease = payment + enganche + op_de_comp
      , income_wservicios = income_lease + seguro_pymnt + legal_fees + maint_pymnt
      , iva_rate = pricing_info_table$GeographyTable$`TaxRate`[which(pricing_info_table$GeographyTable == country_name)] 
      
      #, total_monthly_payment = payment + seguro + legal_fees + enganche + op_de_comp
      , iva = income_wservicios*iva_rate
      , income_total = income_wservicios + iva
      
      ## This is where you apply the payment to socio overtime 
      , capital_costs =
        ifelse(month==0,costo_activo*activo_expense_m1_zz,
               ifelse(month==1,costo_activo*activo_expense_m2_zz,
                      ifelse(month==2,costo_activo*activo_expense_m3_zz
                             ,0)))
      , debt_balance = ifelse(month==0, costo_activo*activo_expense_m1 + other_costs -( payment + enganche + op_de_comp),NA)
      
      , income_qb = income_lease + seguro_pymnt + legal_fees  ## QB doesn't count maint income for some reason (it does it is just 0)
      , iva_payment_qb = income_qb*iva_rate
      , total_received_qb = iva_payment_qb +income_qb
    ) 
  
  for_iva <- (sum(df$income_wservicios) - (sum(df$capital_costs) - sum(df$other_costs) ))*iva_rate/(1+iva_rate)/(loan_term_zz-seguro_start)
  for_iva_qb <- (sum(df$income_qb) - (sum(df$capital_costs) - sum(df$other_costs) ))*iva_rate/(1+iva_rate)/(loan_term_zz-seguro_start)
  ## wtf is this tax calculation --- should it have servicios costs? probably?
  
  df <- df |>
    mutate(
      cost_iva = ifelse(month >= seguro_start & month <= loan_term_zz, for_iva,0)
      , cost_iva_qb = ifelse(month >= seguro_start & month <= loan_term_zz, for_iva_qb,0)
      , expense_qb = capital_costs + other_costs + cost_iva_qb + cost_maint + cost_seguro
      , debt_balance_qb = ifelse(month==0,expense_qb - income_qb,NA)
    )
  
  # calculate debt cost
  for(i in 2:loan_term_zz){
    df$debt_balance[i] = (df$debt_balance[i-1] + df$capital_costs[i]  - df$income_lease[i])*(1+albedo_wacc_zz/12) # Taking lease income rather than income_wservicios
    df$debt_balance_qb[i] = (df$debt_balance_qb[i-1] + df$expense_qb[i]  - df$income_qb[i])*(1+albedo_wacc_zz/12) # Taking lease income
  }
  
  df <- df |>
    mutate(
      lag_db = lag(debt_balance,1),
      , debt_cost = pmax(lag_db*(albedo_wacc_zz/12),0)
      , debt_cost = ifelse(month==0,0,debt_cost)
      , debt_cost_qb = pmax(debt_balance_qb*(albedo_wacc_zz/12),0)
      , debt_cost_qb = ifelse(is.na(debt_balance_qb),0, debt_cost_qb)
    ) |>
    select(-c(lag_db))
  
  # calculate inflows and out-flows
  df <- df |>
    mutate(
      , expense_lease = capital_costs + other_costs
      , expense_lease_wdebt = expense_lease  +  debt_cost
      , expense_wservicios = expense_lease_wdebt + cost_maint + cost_seguro
      , expense_total = expense_wservicios + cost_iva  # currently IVA is in and out 
      , expense_total_qb = expense_qb + debt_cost_qb  
      
      , nii_lease = income_lease - expense_lease
      , nii_lease_wdebt = income_lease - expense_lease_wdebt
      , nii_wservicios = income_wservicios - expense_wservicios
      , nii_total = income_total - expense_total
      , nii_total_qb = total_received_qb - expense_total_qb
      
      , cum_nii_lease = cumsum(nii_lease)
      , cum_nii_lease_wdebt = cumsum(nii_lease_wdebt)
      , cum_nii_wservicios = cumsum(nii_wservicios)
      , cum_nii_total = cumsum(nii_total)
      , cum_nii_total_qb = cumsum(nii_total_qb)
      
      # this makes things easier for duration calc
      , pos_nii_lease_mon = ifelse(month<=2,9999,ifelse(cum_nii_lease<0,9999,month))
      , pos_nii_lease_wdebt_mon = ifelse(month<=2,9999,ifelse(cum_nii_lease_wdebt<0,9999,month))
      , pos_nii_wservicios_mon = ifelse(month<=2,9999,ifelse(cum_nii_wservicios<0,9999,month))
      , pos_nii_total_mon = ifelse(month<=2,9999,ifelse(cum_nii_total<0,9999,month))
      , pos_nii_total_mon_qb = ifelse(month<=2,9999,ifelse(cum_nii_total_qb<0,9999,month))
    )
  
  # NPV
  df <- df |>
    mutate(
      discount_fact = 1/(1+ (risk_free_rate_zz/12))^month
      , npv_nii_lease = discount_fact*nii_lease
      , npv_nii_lease_wdebt = discount_fact*nii_lease_wdebt
      , npv_nii_wservicios = discount_fact*nii_wservicios
      , npv_nii_total = discount_fact*nii_total
      , npv_nii_total_qb = discount_fact*nii_total_qb
    )
  
  
  return(df)
}

#' Examples
#calculate_inc_exp_fun(partial_table,loan_term_zz = term_months, grace_period_zz = grace_period,risk_free_rate_zz=risk_free_rate , albedo_wacc_zz = albedo_wacc)
#calculate_inc_exp_fun(nii_from_db2,loan_term_zz = term_months, grace_period_zz = grace_period,risk_free_rate_zz=risk_free_rate , albedo_wacc_zz = albedo_wacc )

library(shiny) library(shinydashboard) library(bslib) library(dplyr) library(jsonlite) #shinylive::export("C:/Users/imcgr/git/quoting_tool/AlbedoQuoteR", "C:/Users/imcgr/git/ianmcgroarty.github.io/quoting_tool") source('./R/amortization_functions.R') source('./R/pricing_functions.R') source('./R/split_amortization.R') source('./R/calculate_kpis.R') projects <- read.csv("./data/projects_for_app.csv") ## see app_features.Rmd pricing_info_table <- fromJSON("../pricing_info.json") ui <- fluidPage( titlePanel("Quote Generator"), sidebarLayout( sidebarPanel( selectInput("project_select", "Choose a Project:", choices = projects$name, selected = NULL), # Sliders numericInput("costo_activo", "Asset Cost (sin IVA)", value = 115921), sliderInput("duration", "Duration (months):", min = 12, max = 126, value = 12, step = 1), sliderInput("interest_rate", "Interest Rate (%):", min = 10, max = 24, value = 10, step = 0.01), sliderInput("retail_price", "Retail Price:", min = 0, max = 100, value = 50, step = 1), sliderInput("grace_period", "Grace Period (months):", min = 0, max = 5, value = 0, step = 1), sliderInput("down_payment", "Down Payment (%):", min = 0, max = 1, value = 0, step = 0.01) ), mainPanel( layout_column_wrap( value_box( title = "Retail Price", value = uiOutput("retail_price_box"), color = 'green', showcase = icon("dollar-sign"), width = 4) , value_box( title = "Monthly Payment", value = uiOutput("monthly_payment_box"), color = 'orange', #showcase_layout = "middle center", showcase = icon("calendar"), full_screen = TRUE ), value_box( title = "IRR", value = uiOutput("irr_box"), color = 'blue', #showcase_layout = "top right", showcase = icon("leaf") ), width = 1/3 ), tabsetPanel( tabPanel("Client Characteristics", tableOutput("client_table")), tabPanel("Project Characteristics", tableOutput("project_table")), tabPanel("Cash Flow Table", tableOutput("cash_flow_table")), tabPanel("Profit Characteristics", tableOutput("kpi_table"), tableOutput("summary_table")), tabPanel("Global Inputs" , numericInput("op_de_comp_est_pct_zz", "Op de Comp Est %", value = 0.01, min = 0, max = 1, step = 0.01) , numericInput("albedo_wacc_zz", "Albedo WACC", value = 0.10, min = 0, max = 1, step = 0.01) , numericInput("risk_free_rate_zz", "Risk-Free Rate", value = 0.04, min = 0, max = 1, step = 0.01) , numericInput("maint_infl_zz", "Maintenance Inflation", value = 0.05, min = 0, max = 1, step = 0.01) , numericInput("maint_premium_ss", "Maintenance Premium", value = 0, min = 0, max = 1, step = 0.01) , numericInput("seguro_defl_rate_zz", "Seguro Defl Rate", value = 0.96, min = 0, max = 1, step = 0.01) , numericInput("legal_fees_ss", "Legal Fees", value = 2350, min = 0, max = 8000, step = 0.01) , numericInput("maint_cost_per_visit_pct_ss", "Maintenance Cost First Visit", value = 0.0385, min = 0, max = 1, step = 0.01) # NOte need to fix to allow NAs , numericInput("seguro_est_pct_ss", "Seguro Cost First Visit", value = 0.01, min = 0, max = 1, step = 0.01) # NOte need to fix to allow NAs ) # End tab panel ) # end tabset panel ) # end main panel ) # end sidebar layout ) # end fluid page server <- function(input, output, session) { selected_project <- reactive({ req(input$project_select) projects[projects$name == input$project_select, ] }) # --- Update sliders when project changes --- observeEvent(selected_project(), { proj <- selected_project() # Duration updateSliderInput(session, "duration", value = proj$duration) # Interest Rate # Find the interest rate given the monthly payment starting_rate <- find_rate( principal_zz = proj$retail_price_project_currency - proj$down_payment_project_currency, payment_zz = proj$monthly_payment_project_currency, term_zz = (proj$duration - proj$grace_period)*-1 ) updateSliderInput(session, "interest_rate", value = starting_rate) project_cost_up <- reactive({ if(input$project_select == 'Test'){ input$costo_activo } else { proj$project_cost_partner_contract_currency } }) # Retail Price: +/- 10% range retail <- proj$retail_price_project_currency updateSliderInput(session, "retail_price", min = project_cost_up(), max = project_cost_up()*1.5, value = retail) # Grace Period updateSliderInput(session, "grace_period", value = proj$grace_period) }) project_cost_up <- reactive({ proj <- selected_project() if(input$project_select == 'Test'){ input$costo_activo } else { proj$project_cost_partner_contract_currency } }) cash_flow_data <- reactive({ proj <- selected_project() costo_activo <- project_cost_up() partial_table <- calculate_cashflows_fun( # User inputs ann_rate_zz = input$interest_rate/100 , grace_period_zz = input$grace_period , down_payment_pct_zz = input$down_payment , loan_term_zz = input$duration # Pulled from project , area_zz = proj$country_name , costo_activo_zz = costo_activo # calculated , markup_zz = (input$retail_price/costo_activo -1) , costs_zz = input$retail_price*0.03 , legal_fees_zz = input$legal_fees_ss , maint_cost_per_visit_pct_zz = input$maint_cost_per_visit_pct_ss , seguro_est_pct_zz = input$seguro_est_pct_ss # Global variables , op_de_comp_est_pct_zz = 0.01 , albedo_wacc_zz = 0.10 , risk_free_rate_zz = 0.04 , maint_infl_zz = 0.05 , maint_premium_zz = input$maint_premium_ss , seguro_defl_rate_zz = 0.96 ) calculate_inc_exp_fun( partial_table , loan_term_zz = input$duration , grace_period_zz = input$grace_period , risk_free_rate_zz=0.04 , albedo_wacc_zz = 0.09 ) }) kpi_data <- reactive({ get_kpis(cash_flow_data()) }) # --- Score Cards --- output$retail_price_box <- renderText({ proj <- selected_project() costo_activo <- project_cost_up() markup2 <- round(((input$retail_price /costo_activo ) -1 )*100,2) #glue::glue("${(1 - input$pct / 100) * 70} Billion") paste0("Markup: " , formatC(markup2, format="f", big.mark=",", digits = 2), "%" , "
Retail Price: $", formatC(input$retail_price, format = "f", big.mark = ",", digits=0)) }) output$monthly_payment_box <- renderText({ mp <- kpi_data() |> filter(KPI == "Monthly.Payment") |> pull(`Total QB`) paste0("$",formatC(mp[1], format = "f", big.mark = ",", digits=2)) }) # output$impact_score_box <- renderValueBox({ # proj <- selected_project() # proj$impact_score # }) output$irr_box <- renderText({ mp <- kpi_data() |> filter(KPI == "IRR") |> pull(`Total QB`) paste0(formatC(mp[1], format = "f", big.mark = ",", digits=2),"%") }) # --- Tables --- output$client_table <- renderTable({ proj <- selected_project() proj[, c("client_name", "women_led", "non_profit", "rural_area", "youth_led", "educational_institution", "impoverished_area", "country_name", "department_name", "municipality_name")] }) output$project_table <- renderTable({ proj <- selected_project() proj[, c("project_reference", "project_date", "sale_type", "status", "provider_name", "installed_potential_kw", "project_cost_partner_contract_currency", "partner_contract_currency", "retail_price_project_currency", "project_currency")] }) output$kpi_table <- renderTable({ kpi_data() }) output$cash_flow_table <- renderTable({ cash_flow_data() }) output$summary_table <- renderTable({ cash_flow_data() |> summarize( , payment = sum(payment) , principal = sum(principal) , interest = sum(interest) , enganche = sum(enganche) , legal_fees = sum(legal_fees) , op_de_comp = sum(op_de_comp) , cost_seguro = sum(cost_seguro) , cost_maint = sum(cost_maint) , other_costs = sum(other_costs) , seguro_pymnt = sum(seguro_pymnt) , maint_pymnt = sum(maint_pymnt) , debt_cost = sum(debt_cost) , debt_cost_qb = sum(debt_cost_qb) , iva = sum(iva) , iva_payment_qb = sum(iva_payment_qb) , cost_iva = sum(cost_iva) , cost_iva_qb = sum(cost_iva_qb) ) }) } shinyApp(ui, server)

"db.ghulhjlbniwczcmhrysy.supabase.co" , port = 5432 , user = "postgres" , password = my_password ) ``` ```{sql} select * from estimates limit 10 ``` ```{sql} SELECT * retail_price_project_currency retail_price_project_currency FROM static_analytics.mart_projects_overview WHERE 1=1 AND sale_type = 'Financiado' ``` ```{sql, output.var = 'a' } WITH project_info AS ( SELECT p.id AS project_id, p.project_reference, p.name AS project_name, q.contract_signing_date, q.sale_type, c.name AS country_name, e.partner_contract_currency, e.project_currency, e.retail_price_project_currency, e.project_cost_partner_contract_currency, q.monthly_interest_rate FROM projects p JOIN estimates e ON p.id = e.project_id JOIN quotes q ON e.id = q.estimate_id JOIN countries c ON p.country_id = c.id ) , project_calculations AS ( SELECT project_id , COUNT(DISTINCT payment_date) AS duration , COALESCE(SUM(interest_payment_project_currency), 0) AS interest_payment_project_currency , COALESCE(SUM(monthly_payment_project_currency + down_payment_project_currency + asset_transfer_value_project_currency), 0) AS gross_investment , COALESCE(SUM(insurance_payment_project_currency), 0) AS insurance_payment_project_currency , COALESCE(SUM(legal_costs_project_currency), 0) AS legal_costs_project_currency , COALESCE(SUM(monthly_payment_project_currency + down_payment_project_currency + asset_transfer_value_project_currency + insurance_payment_project_currency + legal_costs_project_currency), 0) AS total_contract_value FROM monthly_cash_flows GROUP BY project_id ) --SELECT * FROM project_calculations SELECT * FROM monthly_cash_flows WHERE project_id =1 ``` ```{sql} SELECT --id, project_id, quote_id, payment_number * , down_payment_project_currency + asset_transfer_value_project_currency + interest_payment_project_currency + principal_payment_project_currency AS income_lease , down_payment_project_currency + legal_costs_project_currency + asset_transfer_value_project_currency + interest_payment_project_currency + principal_payment_project_currency + COALESCE(maintenance_payment_project_currency,0) + insurance_payment_project_currency AS income_lease_wservicios , maintenance_cost_project_currency + commission_cost_project_currency + insurance_cost_project_currency AS costs_otras FROM monthly_cash_flows WHERE project_id = 1519 ``` ```{sql, output.var='markupdist'} WITH project_join AS ( SELECT p.id AS project_id, p.project_reference, p.name AS project_name, q.contract_signing_date, q.sale_type, e.partner_contract_currency, e.project_currency, e.retail_price_project_currency, e.project_cost_partner_contract_currency, q.monthly_interest_rate FROM projects p JOIN estimates e ON p.id = e.project_id JOIN quotes q ON e.id = q.estimate_id ) , clean AS ( SELECT project_id , project_name , project_reference , EXTRACT(YEAR FROM contract_signing_date) AS year , sale_type , CASE WHEN partner_contract_currency = 'USD' THEN project_cost_partner_contract_currency*7.8 ELSE project_cost_partner_contract_currency END AS project_cost_gtq , CASE WHEN project_currency = 'USD' THEN retail_price_project_currency*7.8 ELSE retail_price_project_currency END AS retail_price_gtq , monthly_interest_rate*12 AS annual_interest_rate FROM project_join ) SELECT * , ROUND(((retail_price_gtq/project_cost_gtq)-1)*100,1) AS markup FROM clean ``` ```{r} hist(markupdist$markup,20, main = "Markup Distribution", xlab = "Markup %") ``` ```{r} hist((markupdist$annual_interest_rate)*100,20, main = "Interest Rate Distribution", xlab = "Markup %") markupdist |> filter(annual_interest_rate <0 | annual_interest_rate > .40) |> select(project_name, annual_interest_rate) ``` ```{r} markupdist |> arrange(desc(markup)) |> select(project_name, project_cost_gtq, retail_price_gtq, markup) |> filter(markup > 50 | markup <0) ``` ```{sql , output.var = 'project_cashflows'} --, output.var = 'first_passplot' } WITH project_join AS ( SELECT p.id AS project_id, p.project_reference, p.name AS project_name, q.contract_signing_date, q.sale_type, e.partner_contract_currency, e.project_currency, e.retail_price_project_currency, e.project_cost_partner_contract_currency, q.monthly_interest_rate FROM projects p JOIN estimates e ON p.id = e.project_id JOIN quotes q ON e.id = q.estimate_id ) , clean AS ( SELECT project_id , project_name , project_reference , project_currency , EXTRACT(YEAR FROM contract_signing_date) AS year , sale_type , CASE WHEN partner_contract_currency = 'USD' THEN project_cost_partner_contract_currency*1 ELSE project_cost_partner_contract_currency END AS project_cost_gtq , CASE WHEN project_currency = 'USD' THEN retail_price_project_currency*1 ELSE retail_price_project_currency END AS retail_price_gtq , monthly_interest_rate*12 AS annual_interest_rate FROM project_join ) /* SELECT * , ROUND(((retail_price_gtq/project_cost_gtq)-1)*100,1) AS markup FROM clean WHERE project_id IN (554,1574) */ , mcf_data AS ( SELECT id, project_id, quote_id, payment_number, remaining_principal_project_currency , down_payment_project_currency + asset_transfer_value_project_currency + interest_payment_project_currency + principal_payment_project_currency AS income_lease , down_payment_project_currency + legal_costs_project_currency + asset_transfer_value_project_currency + interest_payment_project_currency + principal_payment_project_currency + COALESCE(maintenance_payment_project_currency,0) + insurance_payment_project_currency AS income_lease_wservicios , /*maintenance_cost_project_currency*/ + commission_cost_project_currency + insurance_cost_project_currency AS costs_otras FROM monthly_cash_flows --WHERE project_id = 1519 ) , das_join AS ( SELECT p.project_id , year , sale_type , mcf.payment_number , project_name , CASE WHEN project_currency = 'USD' THEN income_lease*1 ELSE income_lease END AS income_lease , CASE WHEN project_currency = 'USD' THEN income_lease_wservicios*1 ELSE income_lease_wservicios END AS income_lease_wservicios , CASE WHEN project_currency = 'USD' THEN costs_otras*1 ELSE costs_otras END AS costs_otras , project_currency --, CASE WHEN payment_number = 1 THEN project_cost_gtq ELSE 0 END AS , project_cost_gtq --, CASE WHEN payment_number = 1 THEN retail_price_gtq ELSE 0 END AS , retail_price_gtq , p.project_cost_gtq AS project_cost_gtq_alltime , p.retail_price_gtq AS retail_price_gtq_alltime , mcf.remaining_principal_project_currency FROM clean p RIGHT JOIN mcf_data mcf ON p.project_id = mcf.project_id ) , var_create AS ( SELECT * , remaining_principal_project_currency - (retail_price_gtq_alltime - project_cost_gtq_alltime) AS debt_balance , (remaining_principal_project_currency - (retail_price_gtq_alltime - project_cost_gtq_alltime))*0.0075 AS debt_cost , ROUND(costs_otras +project_cost_gtq,1) AS expense_lease FROM das_join ORDER BY project_id, payment_number ) , var_create2 AS ( SELECT * , CASE WHEN debt_cost <0 THEN 0 ELSE debt_cost END AS debt_cost_pos , CASE WHEN debt_cost >0 THEN 9999 ELSE payment_number END AS debt_cost_pos_mon FROM var_create ) , agg_dat AS ( SELECT project_id,project_name, year, sale_type , SUM(income_lease) AS income_lease , SUM(income_lease_wservicios) AS income_lease_wservicios , SUM(costs_otras) AS costs_otras , SUM(project_cost_gtq) AS project_cost_gtq , SUM(retail_price_gtq) AS retail_price_gtq , SUM(debt_cost_pos) AS debt_cost_pos , SUM(project_cost_gtq + debt_cost_pos + costs_otras) AS expense_total , MIN(debt_cost_pos_mon) AS est_payback_period FROM var_create2 GROUP BY project_id,project_name, year, sale_type ) /* SELECT * , income_lease_wservicios - expense_total AS profit_total FROM agg_dat ORDER BY profit_total */ SELECT * FROM var_create2 WHERE 1=1 --AND project_name = 'Hospital San Jorge (El Hato)' ``` ```{sql} --, output.var = 'first_passplot' } WITH project_join AS ( SELECT p.id AS project_id, p.project_reference, q.contract_signing_date, q.sale_type, e.partner_contract_currency, e.project_currency, e.retail_price_project_currency, e.project_cost_partner_contract_currency, q.monthly_interest_rate FROM projects p JOIN estimates e ON p.id = e.project_id JOIN quotes q ON e.id = q.estimate_id ) , clean AS ( SELECT project_id , project_reference , project_currency , EXTRACT(YEAR FROM contract_signing_date) AS year , sale_type , CASE WHEN partner_contract_currency = 'USD' THEN project_cost_partner_contract_currency*7.8 ELSE project_cost_partner_contract_currency END AS project_cost_gtq , CASE WHEN project_currency = 'USD' THEN retail_price_project_currency*7.8 ELSE retail_price_project_currency END AS retail_price_gtq , monthly_interest_rate*12 AS annual_interest_rate FROM project_join ) SELECT * , ROUND(((retail_price_gtq/project_cost_gtq)-1)*100,1) AS markup FROM clean WHERE project_id IN (1584) ``` ```{r} pdat |> filter(est_payback_period > 100) ``` ```{r} pdat <- first_passplot |> filter(sale_type == 'Financiado') |> filter(est_payback_period<1000)|> filter(profit_total < 1000000) |> filter(year == 2025) |> mutate(Gross.Margin = ((income_lease_wservicios-expense_total)/expense_total)*100) |> arrange() plot_ly(type='scatter') |> add_trace(data=pdat, x=~est_payback_period, y=~profit_total , showlegend=FALSE) |> layout( xaxis = list(title = "Payback Period") , yaxis = list(title = "Profit") ) plot_ly(type='scatter') |> add_trace(data=bootstrap_df2 |> filter(Gross.Margin <110 )|> filter(Payback.Period <1000), x=~Payback.Period, y=~Gross.Margin, color=~IRR) |> add_trace(data=pdat , x=~est_payback_period, y=~Gross.Margin , showlegend=FALSE , text = ~paste(project_name, "year: ", year, "
Profit: ", profit_total) , marker = list(size = 10, color = 'rgba(255, 182, 193, .9)', line = list(color = 'rgba(152, 0, 0, .8)', width = 2))) |> layout( xaxis = list(title = "Payback Period") , yaxis = list(title = "Gross Margin") ) ``` ```{r} pdat |> filter(est_payback_period <12 |est_payback_period >120 ) #pdat |> filter(est_payback_period ==63) ``` ```{r} #project_cashflows |> filter(project_name == 'Clinica Sinai') project_cashflows |> filter(project_name == 'Hospital San Jorge (El Hato)') ``` ```{sql} SELECT * FROM monthly_cash_flows --WHERE project_id = 1519 WHERE project_id = 1576 --ORDER BY payment_number ``` ```{sql} SELECT * FROM projects WHERE project_reference = '1407-03' ``` ```{r} write.csv(Hospital, 'hospital_el_hato.csv') ``` ```{sql} SELECT * FROM app.mv_monthly_cash_flows_v1 --WHERE project_id = 1519 --WHERE project_id = 1576 WHERE project_reference = '1407-03' ORDER BY payment_number LIMIT 10 ``` ```{r} pdat |> filter(profit_total <0) pdat |> filter(profit_total >800000) ``` # APR analysis * why is gross investment != cost? * Total legal costs can't be right? ```{sql} Select * , total_finance_income_project_currency/(duration-grace_period) as monthly_finance_payment , total_contract_value_project_currency/(duration-grace_period) as monthly_finance_payment2 from app.mv_projects_v1 where 1=1 and sale_type = 'Financiado' and project_reference = '1407-03' --group by project_currency ``` ```{r} library(plotly) a <- projects |> filter(sale_type == 'Financiado') |> mutate( impactful = ifelse(women_led =='Yes',1,0) , impactful = impactful + ifelse(non_profit =='Yes',1,0) , impactful = impactful + ifelse(rural_area =='Yes',1,0) , impactful = impactful + ifelse(impoverished_area =='Yes',1,0) ) hist((a$monthly_interest_rate_percent)*12,20, main = "Interest Rate Distribution", xlab = "Annual %") ``` ```{r} plot_ly( type='scatter' ) |> add_trace(data=a, x=~duration , y=~monthly_interest_rate_percent*12, color = ~as.factor(impactful)) ``` # Reset ```{sql} SELECT id AS project_id , project_status , status , project_reference , client_name , CASE WHEN project_currency = 'GTQ' AND project_currency = 'USD' THEN project_cost_partner_contract_currency*7.8 END AS project_cost_partner_project_currency , retail_price_project_currency , project_currency , duration , grace_period , monthly_interest_rate_percent/100 AS monthly_rate , monthly_interest_rate_percent*12/100 AS annual_rate , country_name from app.mv_projects_v1 where 1=1 and sale_type = 'Financiado' --and project_reference in ('1407-03', '1885-03') --group by project_currency ``` ```{r} amort_time_form('2000-01-01',98500,.15,48, grace_period_zz = 3) ``` ```{sql} SELECT * from app.mv_projects_v1 limit 10 ``` ```{sql, output.var='nii_from_db2'} --, output.var = 'first_passplot' } WITH project_dat AS ( SELECT id , project_reference , client_name , project_date , project_cost_partner_contract_currency , partner_contract_currency , CASE WHEN project_currency = 'GTQ' AND partner_contract_currency = 'USD' THEN project_cost_partner_contract_currency*7.8 WHEN project_currency = 'GTQ' AND partner_contract_currency = 'GTQ' THEN project_cost_partner_contract_currency WHEN project_currency = 'USD' AND partner_contract_currency = 'USD' THEN project_cost_partner_contract_currency END AS costo_activo , retail_price_project_currency , project_currency , duration , grace_period , monthly_interest_rate_percent/100 AS monthly_rate , monthly_interest_rate_percent*12/100 AS annual_rate , country_name FROM app.mv_projects_v1 WHERE 1=1 AND sale_type = 'Financiado' ) , mcf AS ( SELECT project_id, quote_id , payment_number-1 AS month , remaining_principal_project_currency as ending_principal , down_payment_project_currency AS enganche , legal_costs_project_currency AS legal_fees , asset_transfer_value_project_currency AS op_de_comp , insurance_payment_project_currency AS seguro_pymnt , insurance_cost_project_currency AS cost_seguro , maintenance_cost_project_currency AS cost_maint , COALESCE(maintenance_payment_project_currency,0 ) AS maint_pymnt , interest_payment_project_currency AS interest_accrued , monthly_payment_project_currency AS payment , commission_cost_project_currency AS other_costs FROM monthly_cash_flows --WHERE project_id = 1576 ) , das_join AS ( SELECT p.*, mcf.* FROM project_dat p LEFT JOIN mcf ON p.id = mcf.project_id ) SELECT * FROM das_join ``` ```{r} nii_from_db2 |> head() ``` ```{r} # most people have one payment a bunch have 4/5 and then there are a few others nii_from_db2|> filter(project_reference == '1885-03') ``` ```{r} # Global Options iva_rate <- 0.12 albedo_wacc <- 0.10 risk_free_rate <- 0.04 seguro_defl_rate <- 0.96 seguro_est_pct <- 860.03/56875 op_de_comp_est_pct <- 0.01 commission_cost_est <- (1777.34+444.34)/56875 maint_cost_per_visit_est_pct <- 0.028 maint_inflation_rate_pct <- 0.05 # Timing for cost de activo --- not sure if this is constant across all loans? activo_expense_m1 <- 0.5 activo_expense_m2 <- 0.4 activo_expense_m3 <- 0.1 commission_expense_m1 <- 1 commission_expense_m2 <- 0 commission_expense_m3 <- 00 # Loan Info / Client Options costo_activo <- 56875 down_payment_pct <- 0.00 term_months <- 51 grace_period <- 3 legal_fees <- 0 # Pricing Strat markup <- 73315/56875 - 1 ann_rate <- 0.2040863 maint_premium <- 0.1 target_margin <- 0.05 partial_table <- calculate_cashflows_fun( ann_rate_zz = ann_rate , grace_period_zz = grace_period , markup_zz = markup , down_payment_pct_zz = down_payment_pct , legal_fees_zz = legal_fees , op_de_comp_est_pct_zz = op_de_comp_est_pct , seguro_est_pct_zz = seguro_est_pct , loan_term_zz = term_months , area_zz = 'Guatemala' , costo_activo_zz = costo_activo , costs_zz = other_costs , albedo_wacc_zz = albedo_wacc , risk_free_rate_zz = risk_free_rate , maint_cost_per_visit_pct_zz = maint_cost_per_visit_est_pct , maint_infl_zz = maint_inflation_rate_pct , maint_premium_zz = maint_premium , seguro_defl_rate_zz = seguro_defl_rate ) |> mutate_if(is.numeric, round, 2) calculate_inc_exp_fun(partial_table, term_months, 3,risk_free_rate_zz=0.04 , albedo_wacc_zz= 0.09) ``` ```{r} calculate_inc_exp_fun(nii_from_db2, term_months, 3,risk_free_rate_zz=0.04 , albedo_wacc_zz= 0.09) calculate_inc_exp_fun(nii_from_db2, term_months, 3,risk_free_rate_zz=0.04 , albedo_wacc_zz= 0.09) ``` # Projections ```{r} nii_from_db2 |> #filter(project_currency %in% c('GTQ', 'USD')) |> #select(project_date, month) |> mutate( first_of_month = ymd(format(project_date, "%Y-%m-01")) , next_month = first_of_month %m+% months(month) , ending_principal = ifelse(project_currency == 'GTQ',ending_principal/7.8,ending_principal ) ) |> group_by(next_month) |> summarize( ending_principal = sum(ending_principal) ) |> arrange(next_month) |> filter(next_month == '2025-10-01') ``` ```{r} nii_from_db2 |> #filter(project_date >= '2025-09-01' & project_date < '2025-10-01') |> filter(month == 0 ) |> mutate( retail_price = ifelse(project_currency == 'USD',retail_price_project_currency*7.8,retail_price_project_currency), costo_activo = ifelse(partner_contract_currency == 'USD',project_cost_partner_contract_currency*7.8,project_cost_partner_contract_currency) , year = year(project_date) , month = month(project_date) ) |> group_by(year, month) |> summarize( retail_price = sum(retail_price), costo_activo = sum(costo_activo) + sum(other_costs) ) #pull(retail_price) |> sum() ``` ```{r} nii_from_db2 |> head() ```

--- title: "albedo_pricing" output: html_document --- ```{r setup, include=FALSE} knitr::opts_chunk$set(echo = TRUE) library(dplyr) library(lubridate) library(plotly) library(purrr) library(jrvFinance) library(tidyr) library(jsonlite) ``` ```{r} source('../R/amortization_functions.R') source('../R/pricing_functions.R') source('../R/split_amortization.R') source('../R/calculate_kpis.R') ``` # tables - I want like a list of the inputs, their name/description/official variable name - I want to have the recommended apr and recommended sale markup - everything gets converted to project currency by default, but have a drop down for contract currency, or USD (you want display currency {contract currency, project currency, gtq, usd, colon}) - how to define ranges? - defining the tables and how they relate to each other. - need to do the impact solar savings calculations - Figure out IVA lol - geography table (et al) should be index based. so we can vary the things over time. - We need to draw the app - I need to give Jake & co my recommendation on the projects to pick - I need to finish the project mapping ugh - I need to run the pricing model through the existing loan book (that'll also help me define ranges) - should have a check in with jake - research what other companies to for IRR calc - figure out the maintenance and seguro for out loans. (is geography available to us in DB2)? ```{r} library(readxl) #geography_table <- read_excel("C:\\Users\\imcgr\\Albedo\\Pricing\\Solar Energy Pricing Example.xlsb.xlsx", sheet="Geography Table") #geography_table # Read the JSON file pricing_info_table <- fromJSON("../pricing_info.json") # View the structure# pricing_info_table$GeographyTable #pricing_info_table$TimePremiumLow pricing_info_table$TimePremiumLow$Premium[sum(pricing_info_table$TimePremiumLow$Time <= 40)] default_table <- pricing_info_table$DefaultPremium risk_lvel <- "Low" default_table |> filter(Type == "Enganche") |> pull(risk_lvel) calc_rec_apr("Low", 0.05,enganche_zz = 100, term=12, albedo_wacc_zz = 0.09) ``` ```{r constants} # Global Options iva_rate <- 0.12 albedo_wacc <- 0.10 risk_free_rate <- 0.04 seguro_defl_rate <- 0.96 seguro_est_pct <- 0.017 op_de_comp_est_pct <- 0.01 commission_cost_est <- 0.023 maint_cost_per_visit_est_pct <- 0.028 maint_inflation_rate_pct <- 0.05 # Timing for cost de activo --- not sure if this is constant across all loans? activo_expense_m1 <- 0.5 activo_expense_m2 <- 0.4 activo_expense_m3 <- 0.1 commission_expense_m1 <- 0.8 commission_expense_m2 <- 0 commission_expense_m3 <- 0.2 # Loan Info / Client Options costo_activo <- 398931 down_payment_pct <- 0.00 term_months <- 74 grace_period <- 2 legal_fees <- 2350 # Pricing Strat markup <- 0.0124 ann_rate <- 0.1842 maint_premium <- 0.1 target_margin <- 0.05 # # # Calculated # retail_price <- costo_activo*(1+markup) # down_payment_amt <- retail_price*down_payment_pct # principal <- retail_price*(1-down_payment_pct) # # monthly_rate <- ann_rate/12 # other_costs <- costo_activo*commission_cost_est ## Commission Cost # # seguro_cost_est <- costo_activo*seguro_est_pct ## Seguro # op_de_comp <- retail_price*op_de_comp_est_pct ``` # Bootstrap ```{r} partial_table <- calculate_cashflows_fun( # Pricing Metrics ann_rate_zz = 0.12 , markup_zz = 0.03 # Client Choices , loan_term_zz = 52 , grace_period_zz = grace_period , down_payment_pct_zz = down_payment_pct # Other Costs , legal_fees_zz = legal_fees , op_de_comp_est_pct_zz = op_de_comp_est_pct , seguro_est_pct_zz = seguro_est_pct # Loan Characteristics , area_zz = 'Guatemala' , costo_activo_zz = 100000 , costs_zz = 10000*commission_cost_est , albedo_wacc_zz = albedo_wacc , risk_free_rate_zz = risk_free_rate , maint_cost_per_visit_pct_zz = maint_cost_per_visit_est_pct , maint_infl_zz = maint_inflation_rate_pct , maint_premium_zz = maint_premium , seguro_defl_rate_zz = seguro_defl_rate ) cash_flow_table <- calculate_inc_exp_fun( partial_table , loan_term_zz = 52 , grace_period_zz = 3 , risk_free_rate_zz=risk_free_rate , albedo_wacc_zz = albedo_wacc ) cash_flow_table |> get_kpis() |> pull(`Leasing w Debt`) ``` ```{r} # Income Sources cash_flow_table |> summarize( , payment = sum(payment) , principal = sum(principal) , interest = sum(interest) , enganche = sum(enganche) , legal_fees = sum(legal_fees) , op_de_comp = sum(op_de_comp) , cost_seguro = sum(cost_seguro) , cost_maint = sum(cost_maint) , other_costs = sum(other_costs) , seguro_pymnt = sum(seguro_pymnt) , maint_pymnt = sum(maint_pymnt) , debt_cost = sum(debt_cost) , debt_cost_qb = sum(debt_cost_qb) ) ``` ```{r} kpis_boostrap_fun <- function(term_z,apr_z, costo_activo_z, markup_z = 0.0124 ){ partial_table <- calculate_cashflows_fun( # Pricing Metrics ann_rate_zz = apr_z , markup_zz = markup_z # Client Choices , loan_term_zz = term_z , grace_period_zz = grace_period , down_payment_pct_zz = down_payment_pct # Other Costs , legal_fees_zz = legal_fees , op_de_comp_est_pct_zz = op_de_comp_est_pct , seguro_est_pct_zz = seguro_est_pct # Loan Characteristics , area_zz = 'Guatemala' , costo_activo_zz = costo_activo_z , costs_zz = costo_activo_z*commission_cost_est , albedo_wacc_zz = albedo_wacc , risk_free_rate_zz = risk_free_rate , maint_cost_per_visit_pct_zz = maint_cost_per_visit_est_pct , maint_infl_zz = maint_inflation_rate_pct , maint_premium_zz = maint_premium , seguro_defl_rate_zz = seguro_defl_rate ) a <- calculate_inc_exp_fun( partial_table , loan_term_zz = term_z , grace_period_zz = grace_period , risk_free_rate_zz=risk_free_rate , albedo_wacc_zz = albedo_wacc ) |> get_kpis() |> pull(`Leasing w Debt`) return(a) } kpis_boostrap_fun(term_z = 12,apr_z = 0.08,costo_activo_z = 10000) ``` ```{r} set.seed(123) n <- 1000 #terms <- sample(12:200, n, replace = TRUE) # loan terms from 1 to 10 years terms <- rep(24,n) aprs <- runif(n, min = 0.1, max = 0.25) # APRs from 1% to 15% #aprs <- rep(0.18,n) #sizes <- runif(n, min = 5000, max = 500000) # loan sizes from $5k to $500k sizes <- rep(10000,n) #markups <- rep(markup,n) markups <- runif(n, min = 0.0, max = 0.25) # Create empty matrix to store results results_matrix <- matrix(NA, nrow = n, ncol = 8) colnames(results_matrix) <- c("Income", "Expense", "Profit", "Net Present Value", "IRR", "Gross Margin", "Payback Period", "Monthly Payment") # Run loop for (i in seq_len(n)) { metrics <- kpis_boostrap_fun( term_z = terms[i],apr_z= aprs[i],costo_activo_z= sizes[i],markup_z = markups[i] ) results_matrix[i, ] <- metrics } # Combine into final dataframe bootstrap_df_aprXmargin24 <- data.frame( term = terms, apr = aprs, size = sizes, markup = markups, results_matrix ) ``` ```{r} get_kpis() ``` ```{r} #term #plot_ly(type='scatter') |> # add_trace(data=bootstrap_df, x=~Payback.Period, y=~Profit, color=~term) # term v apr # plot_ly(type='scatter') |> # add_trace(data=bootstrap_df2, x=~Payback.Period, y=~Profit, color=~IRR) ## Size v term #plot_ly(type='scatter') |> # add_trace(data=bootstrap_df3, x=~Payback.Period, y=~Profit, color=~size) ## size v APR (for given term) #plot_ly(type='scatter') |> # add_trace(data=bootstrap_df4, x=~Payback.Period, y=~Profit, color=~IRR) # # APR x Margin # plot_ly(type='scatter') |> # add_trace(data=bootstrap_df_aprXmargin60, x=~apr, y=~markup, color=~Monthly.Payment) # # # # plot_ly(type='scatter') |> # add_trace(data=bootstrap_df_aprXmargin60, x=~IRR, y=~Monthly.Payment, name = 'term = 60' ) |> # add_trace(data=bootstrap_df_aprXmargin48, x=~IRR, y=~Monthly.Payment, name = 'term = 48' ) ``` # Predict IRR given APR and Margin ```{r} x <- c(8,35) y = x*1.2 -10 plot_ly(type='scatter') |> add_trace(data=bootstrap_df_aprXmargin72 |> filter(markup <0.1) , x=~apr*100, y=~IRR, color = ~markup ) |> add_trace( x = x, # adjust range to match your data y = y, # same range for y mode = "lines", line = list(color = "black", dash = "dash"), name = "45 line" ) plot_ly(type='scatter') |> add_trace(data=bootstrap_df_aprXmargin48 |> filter(markup <0.1) , x=~apr*100, y=~IRR, color = ~markup ) |> add_trace( x = x, # adjust range to match your data y = y, # same range for y mode = "lines", line = list(color = "black", dash = "dash"), name = "45 line" ) ``` ```{r} a <- bootstrap_df_aprXmargin72 |> filter(markup <0.1) |> mutate(apr = apr*100) |> mutate( markup_pct = round(markup*100,0) , markup_str = as.character(markup_pct) ) fit <- lm(IRR ~ apr + markup_str , data = a) summary(fit) ``` # Predict Margin given APR and IRR ```{r} x <- c(0,.15) y = x*-2.5 +.35 # plot_ly(type='scatter') |> # add_trace(data=bootstrap_df_aprXmargin48 |> filter(IRR>5 & IRR <7) # , x=~apr, y=~markup, color=~IRR)|> # add_trace(data=bootstrap_df_aprXmargin60 |> filter(IRR>5 & IRR <7) # , x=~apr, y=~markup, color=~IRR) |> # layout( # yaxis = list(range=c(0,.14)) # ) plot_ly(type='scatter') |> add_trace(data=bootstrap_df_aprXmargin60 |> filter(IRR>1 & IRR <10) , x=~apr, y=~markup, color=~IRR , text = ~paste("IRR: ", IRR) ) |> layout( yaxis = list(range=c(0,.2)), xaxis = list(range=c(.08,.2)) ) |> add_trace( x = x, # adjust range to match your data y = y, # same range for y mode = "lines", line = list(color = "black", dash = "dash"), name = "45 line" ) ``` ```{r} a <- bootstrap_df_aprXmargin24 |> filter(IRR <13 & IRR >1) |> mutate( irr_pct = round(IRR,0) , irr_str = as.character(irr_pct) ) fit <- lm(markup ~ apr + irr_str , data = a) summary(fit) ``` ```{r} lazaro <- c("Lazaro", 61683.72 , 49827.45, 11856.28 , 4438.72 , 12.02, 41, 24) doris <- c("Doris Zuniga", 291995.10 , 222066.72, 69928.39 , 21713.93 , 11.18, 63, 31) roberto <- c("Roberto Santa", 77866.76 , 60109.18, 17757.58 , 6454.15 , 12.21, 55, 30) santos <- c("Eliasin Santos", 26793.02 , 23639.45, 3153.57 , 313.29 , 7.87, 44, 13) INMSA <- c("INMSA ARGO", 307336.36 , 250697.10, 56639.26 , 6357.12 , 8.06, 61, 23) castellon <-c("Castellon" , 330418.90 , 214464.99, 115953.91 , 50218.83 , 15.08, 59, 54) proyectos <- data.frame(rbind(lazaro,doris, roberto, santos, INMSA)) names(proyectos) <- c("Project", "Income", "Expense", "Profit", "NPV", "IRR", "Payback.Period", "Gross.Margin") proyectos ``` ```{r} plot_ly(type='scatter') |> add_trace(data=bootstrap_df2 |> filter(Payback.Period <500), x=~Payback.Period, y=~Profit, color=~IRR) |> add_trace(data=proyectos, x=~Payback.Period, y=~Profit , text = ~paste(Project, "IRR: ", IRR, "
Margin: ", Gross.Margin) , marker = list(size = 10, color = 'rgba(255, 182, 193, .9)', line = list(color = 'rgba(152, 0, 0, .8)', width = 2))) ``` ```{r} plot_ly(type='scatter') |> add_trace(data=bootstrap_df2 |> filter(Payback.Period < 500), x=~Payback.Period, y=~Gross.Margin, color=~IRR) |> add_trace(data=proyectos, x=~Payback.Period, y=~Gross.Margin , text = ~paste(Project, "IRR: ", IRR, "
Margin: ", Gross.Margin) , marker = list(size = 10, color = 'rgba(255, 182, 193, .9)', line = list(color = 'rgba(152, 0, 0, .8)', width = 2))) ``` ```{r} get_kpis( calculate_inc_exp_fun( a , loan_term_zz = a$duration[1] , a$grace_period[1] , risk_free_rate_zz=0.04 , albedo_wacc_zz= 0.09 ) ) ``` # Running portfolio through KPIs ```{r} a <- nii_from_db2 |> filter(project_reference == '1558-01') |> arrange(month) project_kpis <- get_kpis( calculate_inc_exp_fun( a , loan_term_zz = a$duration[1] , a$grace_period[1] , risk_free_rate_zz=0.04 , albedo_wacc_zz= 0.09 ) ) |> mutate(project_reference = '255-01') skip <- c('255-01') project_ids <- unique(nii_from_db2$project_reference)[!unique(nii_from_db2$project_reference) %in% bad] for(p in project_ids ){ nii_tab_t <- nii_from_db2 |> filter(project_reference == p) |> arrange(month) project_kpis <- rbind(project_kpis, get_kpis( calculate_inc_exp_fun( nii_tab_t , loan_term_zz = nii_tab_t$duration[1] , nii_tab_t$grace_period[1] , risk_free_rate_zz=0.04 , albedo_wacc_zz= 0.09 ) ) |> mutate(project_reference = p) ) } a <- nii_from_db2 |> filter(month == 1) |> select(project_reference, client_name,project_date) #,retail_price_project_currency,project_cost_partner_contract_currency, partner_contract_currency, project_currency, duration, annual_rate, country_name ) project_kpis <- left_join(project_kpis, a , by = 'project_reference') write.csv(project_kpis, 'financed_projects_kpis.csv') ``` ```{r} project_kpis_wide <- project_kpis |> filter(year(project_date)>=2025) |> select(KPI, `Total QB`, project_reference) |> pivot_wider(names_from = KPI, values_from = `Total QB`) |> filter(Payback.Period < 1000) plot_ly(type='scatter') |> add_trace(data=bootstrap_df2 |> filter(Payback.Period < 500), x=~Payback.Period, y=~Gross.Margin, color=~IRR) |> add_trace(data=project_kpis_wide, x=~Payback.Period, y=~Gross.Margin , text = ~paste(project_reference, "IRR: ", IRR, "
Margin: ", Gross.Margin) , marker = list(size = 10, color = 'rgba(255, 182, 193, .9)' , line = list(color = 'rgba(152, 0, 0, .8)', width = 2))) ``` ```{r} a <- nii_from_db2 |> filter(project_reference == '1928-01') |> arrange(month) #project_kpis <- get_kpis( calculate_inc_exp_fun( a , loan_term_zz = a$duration[1] , a$grace_period[1] , risk_free_rate_zz=0.04 , albedo_wacc_zz= 0.09 ) #) |> mutate(project_reference = '255-01') ``` # my boi ```{r} # cesar nii_table_fun( ann_rate_zz = 0.1842 , grace_period_zz = 2 , markup_zz = 0.012388107 , down_payment_pct_zz = 0 , enganche_zz = 0 , legal_fees_zz = 2350 , op_de_comp_est_pct_zz = 0.0103 #, seguro_est_pct_zz = seguro_est_pct , loan_term_zz = 74 , area_zz = 'GT' , costo_activo_zz = 398931 , costs_zz = 9015 , albedo_wacc_zz = .1 , risk_free_rate_zz = risk_free_rate , maint_cost_per_visit_pct_zz = NA , maint_infl_zz = maint_inflation_rate_pct , maint_premium_zz = maint_premium , seguro_defl_rate_zz = seguro_defl_rate ) |> mutate_if(is.numeric, round, 2) ``` # OLD ## Net Income Table ```{r old} nii_table_fun <- function( legal_fees_zz, op_de_comp_est_pct_zz , ann_rate_zz = NA, loan_term_zz, grace_period_zz, markup_zz, down_payment_pct_zz , seguro_est_pct_zz = NA , seguro_defl_rate_zz , maint_premium_zz, maint_cost_per_visit_pct_zz = NA, maint_infl_zz , costo_activo_zz, costs_zz , albedo_wacc_zz, risk_free_rate_zz , area_zz = 'Guatemala', risk_level_zz = 'Low', target_margin_zz = 0 ){ # Lookup Fields iva_rate <-pricing_info_table$GeographyTable$`TaxRate`[which(pricing_info_table$GeographyTable == area_zz)] if (is.na(seguro_est_pct_zz )){ seguro_pct <- pricing_info_table$GeographyTable$`Insurance`[which(pricing_info_table$GeographyTable$Area == area_zz)] } else { seguro_pct <- seguro_est_pct_zz } if (is.na(maint_cost_per_visit_pct_zz )){ maint_cost_per_visit_pct <- pricing_info_table$GeographyTable$`Maintenance`[which(pricing_info_table$GeographyTable$Area == area_zz)] } else { maint_cost_per_visit_pct <- maint_cost_per_visit_pct_zz } ## recommended APR rec_apr <- calc_rec_apr(risk_level_zz, target_margin_zz,down_payment_pct_zz , loan_term_zz, albedo_wacc_zz) if(is.na(ann_rate_zz)) { annual_APR <- rec_apr } else { annual_APR <- ann_rate_zz } # Calculated Fields maint_cost_per_visit <- maint_cost_per_visit_pct*costo_activo_zz seguro_start <- grace_period + 1 retail_price <- costo_activo_zz*(1+markup_zz) down_payment_amt <- retail_price*down_payment_pct_zz principal <- retail_price*(1-down_payment_amt) monthly_rate <- annual_APR/12 seguro_cost_est <- costo_activo_zz*seguro_pct ## Seguro op_de_comp <- retail_price*op_de_comp_est_pct_zz finance_table <- amort_time_form('2000-01-01',principal,annual_APR,loan_term_zz,grace_period_zz) df <- finance_table %>% mutate( enganche = ifelse(month == 0, down_payment_amt, 0) , legal_fees = ifelse(month == 0, legal_fees_zz, 0) , op_de_comp = ifelse(month== loan_term_zz, op_de_comp,0) , cost_seguro = ifelse((12-seguro_start+month) %% 12 != 0,0 , ifelse(month>loan_term_zz,0 , seguro_cost_est*seguro_defl_rate_zz^(floor(month/12)) )) , cost_maint = ifelse(month <= 24,0 ## Doesn't cost anything for first 2 years ,ifelse(month> loan_term_zz, 0 ,ifelse(month %% 12 != 0, 0 ,maint_cost_per_visit*(1+maint_infl_zz)^(pmax(floor(month / 12 - 3), 0)) ))) , other_costs = ifelse(month==0,costs_zz*commission_expense_m1, ifelse(month==1,costs_zz*commission_expense_m2, ifelse(month==2,costs_zz*commission_expense_m3 ,0))) ) # Calculate the maintenence and insurance payments total_main_cost <- sum(df$cost_maint)*(1+maint_premium_zz) maint_pymnt <- total_main_cost/(loan_term_zz-seguro_start+1) total_seguro_cost <- sum(df$cost_seguro) seguro_pymnt <- total_seguro_cost/(loan_term_zz-seguro_start+1) df <- df |> mutate( , seguro_pymnt = ifelse(month >= seguro_start & month <= loan_term_zz, seguro_pymnt,0) , maint_pymnt = ifelse(month >= seguro_start & month <= loan_term_zz, maint_pymnt,0) , income_lease = payment + enganche + op_de_comp , income_wservicios = income_lease + seguro_pymnt + legal_fees + maint_pymnt #, total_monthly_payment = payment + seguro + legal_fees + enganche + op_de_comp , iva = income_wservicios*iva_rate , income_total = income_wservicios + iva , capital_costs = ifelse(month==0,costo_activo_zz*activo_expense_m1, ifelse(month==1,costo_activo_zz*activo_expense_m2, ifelse(month==2,costo_activo_zz*activo_expense_m3 ,0))) , debt_balance = ifelse(month==0, costo_activo_zz*activo_expense_m1 + other_costs -( payment + enganche + op_de_comp),NA) , income_qb = income_lease + seguro_pymnt + legal_fees ## QB doessn't count maint income for some reason , iva_payment_qb = income_qb*iva_rate ) for_iva <- (sum(df$income_wservicios) - (sum(df$capital_costs) - sum(df$other_costs) ))*iva_rate/(1+iva_rate)/(loan_term_zz-seguro_start) for_iva_qb <- (sum(df$income_qb) - (sum(df$capital_costs) - sum(df$other_costs) ))*iva_rate/(1+iva_rate)/(loan_term_zz-seguro_start) ## wtf is this tax calculation df <- df |> mutate( cost_iva = ifelse(month >= seguro_start & month <= loan_term_zz, for_iva,0) , cost_iva_qb = ifelse(month >= seguro_start & month <= loan_term_zz, for_iva_qb,0) , expense_qb = capital_costs + other_costs + cost_iva_qb + cost_maint + cost_seguro , debt_balance_qb = ifelse(month==0,expense_qb - income_qb,NA) ) # calculate debt cost for(i in 2:loan_term_zz){ df$debt_balance[i] = (df$debt_balance[i-1] + df$capital_costs[i] - df$income_lease[i])*(1+albedo_wacc_zz/12) # Taking lease income rather than income_wservicios df$debt_balance_qb[i] = (df$debt_balance_qb[i-1] + df$expense_qb[i] - df$income_qb[i])*(1+albedo_wacc_zz/12) # Taking lease income } df <- df |> mutate( lag_db = lag(debt_balance,1), , debt_cost = pmax(lag_db*(albedo_wacc_zz/12),0) , debt_cost = ifelse(month==0,0,debt_cost) , debt_cost_qb = pmax(debt_balance_qb*(albedo_wacc_zz/12),0) ) |> select(-c(lag_db)) # calculate inflows and out-flows df <- df |> mutate( , expense_lease = capital_costs + other_costs , expense_lease_wdebt = expense_lease + debt_cost , expense_wservicios = expense_lease_wdebt + cost_maint + cost_seguro , expense_total = expense_wservicios + cost_iva # currently IVA is in and out , nii_lease = income_lease - expense_lease , nii_lease_wdebt = income_lease - expense_lease_wdebt , nii_wservicios = income_wservicios - expense_wservicios , nii_total = income_total - expense_total , cum_nii_lease = cumsum(nii_lease) , cum_nii_lease_wdebt = cumsum(nii_lease_wdebt) , cum_nii_wservicios = cumsum(nii_wservicios) , cum_nii_total = cumsum(nii_total) # this makes things easier for duration calc , pos_nii_lease_mon = ifelse(cum_nii_lease<0,9999,month) , pos_nii_lease_wdebt_mon = ifelse(cum_nii_lease_wdebt<0,9999,month) , pos_nii_wservicios_mon = ifelse(cum_nii_wservicios<0,9999,month) , pos_nii_total_mon = ifelse(cum_nii_total<0,9999,month) ) # NPV df <- df |> mutate( discount_fact = 1/(1+ (risk_free_rate_zz/12))^month , npv_nii_lease = discount_fact*nii_lease , npv_nii_lease_wdebt = discount_fact*nii_lease_wdebt , npv_nii_wservicios = discount_fact*nii_wservicios , npv_nii_total = discount_fact*nii_total ) return(df) } nii_tab <- nii_table_fun( ann_rate_zz = ann_rate , grace_period_zz = grace_period , markup_zz = markup , down_payment_pct_zz = down_payment_pct , legal_fees_zz = legal_fees , op_de_comp_est_pct_zz = op_de_comp_est_pct #, seguro_est_pct_zz = seguro_est_pct , loan_term_zz = term_months , area_zz = 'Guatemala' , costo_activo_zz = costo_activo , costs_zz = other_costs , albedo_wacc_zz = albedo_wacc , risk_free_rate_zz = risk_free_rate , maint_cost_per_visit_pct_zz = maint_cost_per_visit_est_pct , maint_infl_zz = maint_inflation_rate_pct , maint_premium_zz = maint_premium , seguro_defl_rate_zz = seguro_defl_rate ) |> mutate_if(is.numeric, round, 2) #nii_tab |> mutate_if(is.numeric,round, 1) |> # select(-c(principal, interest, interest_accrued, # enganche,legal_fees,op_de_comp ,other_costs # , cost_seguro, cost_maint, seguro_pymnt, maint_pymnt # ,balance, payment, iva, capital_costs # )) # a <- get_kpis(nii_tab) a$`Total w IVA` a ``` ```{r} costo_activo <- 85000 markup <- 0.05 retail_price <- costo_activo*(1+markup) down_payment_pct <- 0.015 down_payment_amt <- retail_price*down_payment_pct principal <- retail_price*(1-down_payment_pct) ann_rate <- 0.165 monthly_rate <- ann_rate/12 term_months <- 48 grace_period <- 3 finance_table <- amort_time_form('2000-01-01',principal,ann_rate,term_months) legal_fees <- 1000 op_de_comp <- 2500 seguro <- 300 seguro_start <- 5 other_costs <- 23341 iva_rate <- 0.12 albedo_wacc <- 0.09 risk_free_rate <- 0.04 # Timing for cost de activ0 activo_expense_m1 <- 0.5 activo_expense_m2 <- 0.4 activo_expense_m3 <- 0.1 # Excluding maintenance for now, I think honestly what we should do is the full maint cost/360 it'll just be easier # probably should do like 5 year increments. #maint_cost_year_pct <- 0.02 #maint_cost_year <- maint_cost_year_pct*costo_activo #maint_premium <- 0.1 #maint_freq_year <- 2 nii_tab <- nii_table_fun( amort_table_zz = finance_table , enganche_zz = down_payment_amt , legal_fees_zz = legal_fees , op_de_comp_zz = op_de_comp , seguro_zz = seguro , seguro_start_mon_zz = seguro_start , loan_term_zz = term_months , costo_activo_zz = costo_activo , costs_zz = other_costs , albedo_wacc_zz = albedo_wacc , risk_free_rate_zz = risk_free_rate ) nii_tab |> mutate_if(is.numeric,round,1) ``` ```{r} npv <- sum(nii_tab$npv_nii) npv_wdebt <- sum(nii_tab$npv_nii_wdebt) monthly_irr <- jrvFinance::irr(nii_tab$net_inflow) annual_irr <-monthly_irr*12 duration <- nii_tab |> filter(cumulative_inflow >=0) |> pull(month) |> min() total_rec <- sum(nii_tab$total_monthly_payment) total_costs <- sum(nii_tab$total_cost) total_costs_wdebt <- sum(nii_tab$total_cost_wdebt, na.rm=TRUE) gross_margin <- (total_rec-total_costs)/total_costs gross_margin_wdebt <- (total_rec-total_costs_wdebt)/total_costs_wdebt gross_margin_wdebt ``` ```{r} amort_form(102240.11,102240.11,.15,48-3) ``` # Questions - I still don't understand when legal fees are accounted for? It looks like they are getting swooped up but then they are making the payment in the month/ - Maint. income over 30 years - IRR with/without debt payments. - Measuring "Other Costs" - commissions - servicing Maintenance is going to be hard to make actually profitable - how should we handle the payment (annual or included in monthly paymnet) - estimating other costs - estimating seguro? -- do commission costs go into IRR -- do maint payment/cost go into IRR? -- do servicios go into debt ```{r} mortgage <- 300000 duration <- 360 ann <- 1108.86 uniroot(function(x) mortgage * x/12 / (1 - (1+x/12)^(-duration)) - ann, c(1e-6,1))$root * 100 find_rate <- function(principal_zz, payment_zz, term_zz){ f <- function(r) (principal_zz *r / (1-(1+r)^term_zz) ) - payment_zz sol <- uniroot(f, interval = c(1e-6,1)) return(monthly_rate = sol$root*100*12) } find_rate(principal_zz = mortgage,payment_zz = ann, term_zz= -1*duration ) ```

WITH first_dat AS (
 SELECT  
 p.name,
 
 client_id, client_name, 
 women_led, non_profit, rural_area, youth_led, educational_institution, impoverished_area
  , CASE WHEN women_led = 'Yes' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS women_led_score
  , CASE WHEN non_profit = 'Yes' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS non_profit_score
  , CASE WHEN rural_area = 'Yes' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS rural_area_score
  , CASE WHEN youth_led = 'Yes' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS youth_led_score
  , CASE WHEN educational_institution = 'Yes' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS educational_institution_score
  , CASE WHEN impoverished_area = 'Yes' THEN 1 ELSE 0 END AS impoverished_area_score
 , country_name, department_name, municipality_name,country_id,
 
 
 project_reference,id ,project_date, sale_type, status, 
  provider_name, installed_potential_kw,
  
 project_cost_partner_contract_currency, partner_contract_currency,
 retail_price_project_currency,project_currency 
 , monthly_payment_project_currency, duration, grace_period
 , monthly_interest_rate_percent*12 AS interest_rate
 , down_payment_project_currency
 
 
  FROM app.mv_projects_v1 p 

  LEFT JOIN (SELECT project_id, down_payment_project_currency, monthly_payment_project_currency FROM monthly_cash_flows WHERE payment_number = 5) mcf
    ON p.id = mcf.project_id

  WHERE 1=1
  AND sale_type = 'Financiado'
  AND project_date >= '2025-01-01'
  )
  
  SELECT * ,
    women_led_score + non_profit_score + rural_area_score + youth_led_score + educational_institution_score + impoverished_area_score AS impact_score
  FROM first_dat
